WEBVTT

00:01.512 --> 00:03.219
[Axe] Previously
on Billions...

00:03.221 --> 00:04.554
I thought
I would outlast you.

00:04.555 --> 00:05.845
I was wrong
about Axe.

00:05.846 --> 00:06.886
He's backing me.

00:06.887 --> 00:08.262
I'm waving the white flag.

00:08.263 --> 00:09.251
Willing to go back
to supplying you.

00:09.253 --> 00:11.001
You cut a fucking deal
with Taylor?

00:11.002 --> 00:12.418
I saw the friction

00:12.419 --> 00:14.418
that it already
had created between us.

00:14.419 --> 00:16.085
So I let you
off the hook.

00:16.085 --> 00:18.459
We are here today to explore
serious charges

00:18.460 --> 00:19.626
against
Doctor Wendy Rhoades.

00:19.627 --> 00:21.001
If she acted in
a medical capacity--

00:21.002 --> 00:22.418
I did.

00:22.419 --> 00:24.335
- [door bangs]
- FBI! Let me see your hands!

00:24.336 --> 00:25.501
[baby crying]

00:25.502 --> 00:28.127
Don't you
lay a hand on her!

00:28.128 --> 00:29.584
If you answer
my questions,

00:29.585 --> 00:31.584
neither you nor your boy
need be clapped in iron.

00:31.585 --> 00:34.751
I'm not saying a damn thing
to help you hurt my boy.

00:34.752 --> 00:36.584
Have I ever told you

00:36.585 --> 00:38.584
when I knew that you were gonna
be my partner at all this.

00:38.585 --> 00:40.001
You remember?

00:40.002 --> 00:42.001
What kind of man would I be
if I didn't?

00:42.002 --> 00:44.709
Chuck, when did you know
you needed to marry me?

00:44.710 --> 00:48.335
I mean the--the exact
moment.

00:48.336 --> 00:50.543
I don't remember.

00:50.544 --> 00:53.543
The kind of destruction
you're considering,

00:53.544 --> 00:56.335
the relationships
that'll be ruined--

00:56.336 --> 00:57.543
you ready for all that?

00:57.544 --> 00:58.709
What else is on
the unredacted tape?

00:58.710 --> 01:00.210
What, exactly, was getting
locked in the safe?

01:00.211 --> 01:02.043
Bryan! Stop pushing me.

01:02.044 --> 01:03.918
They were dancing around
whatever they were doing--

01:03.919 --> 01:05.627
if there's documentation
to be retrieved...

